column5: I've got a couple of walleye fishing trips coming up in the Abitibi/Témiscaming area of Quebec. Once we get to Mattawa, we usually travel highway 533 from Mattawa to highway 63 on our way to Témiscaming.  Can anyone report on the condition of highway 533 please. Thanks in advance.
I havent been on it this year but that road is well traveled and is kept in good shape. Up until last year i had a trailer in Mattawa and i regularly used that road with no problem.  vance
